---
const faqs = [
  {
    question: "How does CARAUKTION Direct work?",
    answer: "Private sellers list their cars on our platform. As a registered dealer, you can view detailed information about each vehicle, place bids, and participate in auctions. Once you win an auction, we handle all the paperwork and logistics to ensure a smooth transaction."
  },
  {
    question: "What types of vehicles are available?",
    answer: "We offer a wide range of vehicles from private sellers across Switzerland, including passenger cars, SUVs, and light commercial vehicles. All vehicles undergo a thorough verification process before being listed."
  },
  {
    question: "How are vehicle conditions verified?",
    answer: "Each vehicle listed on CARAUKTION Direct undergoes a comprehensive inspection by our certified partners. Detailed condition reports, including photos and documentation, are provided for every auction listing."
  },
  {
    question: "What are the costs involved?",
    answer: "Registration for dealers is free. When you successfully win an auction, a transparent buyer's premium is applied. There are no hidden fees, and all costs are clearly displayed before bidding."
  },
  {
    question: "How long do auctions typically last?",
    answer: "Most auctions run for 24-48 hours, giving you enough time to review the vehicle details and place your bids. The exact duration is always displayed on each auction listing."
  },
  {
    question: "Is there a mobile app available?",
    answer: "Yes, we offer a dedicated mobile app for both iOS and Android devices. You can participate in auctions, receive notifications, and manage your account on the go."
  },
  {
    question: "What happens after winning an auction?",
    answer: "Once you win an auction, our team handles all the necessary paperwork and coordinates the vehicle transfer. You'll receive detailed instructions and support throughout the process."
  }
];
---

<section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl divide-y divide-gray-200">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-text-primary sm:text-4xl">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-text-secondary">
          Everything you need to know about buying cars through CARAUKTION Direct
        </p>
      </div>
      <dl class="mt-10 space-y-6 divide-y divide-gray-200">
        {faqs.map((faq) => (
          <div class="pt-6">
            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex w-full items-start justify-between text-left cursor-pointer">
                <span class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary">{faq.question}</span>
                <span class="ml-6 flex h-7 items-center">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6 rotate-0 transform text-text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5" />
                  </svg>
                </span>
              </summary>
              <div class="mt-4 pr-12">
                <p class="text-base text-text-secondary">{faq.answer}</p>
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>
        ))}
      </dl>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  details > summary {
    list-style: none;
  }
  details > summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }
</style>